@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
    This application is a demonstration IT Knowledge Base Assistant.
    It is intended for educational and evaluation purposes only.
</p>

<h2>Data Collection</h2>
<p>
    The application does not store personal data. User questions are processed
    temporarily to generate responses and are not persisted in a database.
</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>
    User questions and relevant documentation snippets are sent to a third-party
    Large Language Model (LLM) API solely for the purpose of generating an answer.
    No personal user identification information is included intentionally.
</p>

<h2>Data Storage</h2>
<p>
    Generated answers may be cached in memory during application runtime to
    improve performance. This cache is cleared when the application restarts.
</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>
    If you have questions about this application, please contact the system administrator.
</p>
